@baseURL = http://localhost:9000/api/pipelines

### Get all pipelines
GET {{baseURL}}/configs  HTTP/1.1

### Get pipeline x
@pipelineid = 3
GET {{baseURL}}/configs/{{pipelineid}}  HTTP/1.1

